column5: Few bass I caught end of Aug early Sept before weather went crazy!...All on senkos...Used senkos pretty much all season long with excellect success!!
Nice bass' Thanks for sharing Leechman
Awesome fish! I hope you got more than 3   Jood job.
Very nice!But those pictures dont do the fish justice. Try posting them on photobucket or something.

Ya I had to cut to reduce size so I could post...not that high tech... these were the ones I took that i had a camera with me....caught a nice smalley just over 4lb - great fight and couple of nice size largies....a tone of 1.5- 2.5 lbers too...got to learn photobucket or what ever cause i see other posts with a bunch of pics!! thx guys!
